location.fullValue: The Wildflower II Plan, Summerfields West - An Active Adult Community 55+

data.description: Welcome to your new home!!! This updated  2 bed, 2 bath includes a sunroom, sizable kitchen with tons of storage, separate spacious dining room and living room with the open concept you have been looking for and 2 driveways for your convenience. There is a bathroom on each floor and the sunroom could easily be converted into an in-law suite! Step outback to an over sized yard waiting for you to entertain in. The home also backs up to a unique & serene 6 mile walking/bike path. Equipped with an adorable front porch, curb appeal is not an issue here. Both water heater and partial roof are less than 10 years old. Flat roof replaced this year. In a market with low inventory, don't miss your opportunity to come drop your bags and move right in to this gem. Sellers are under contract and looking to close on the same day as this sale.
